Just got back from having burgers at Harvey's and I am BLOWN AWAY! Haven't been for a while and decided today was the day to rekindle our friendship :) The burgers are AMAZING!!! We had the rodeo burger and the garlic patty melt which had to be one of the best things I've ever eaten!!! I am worried that I will be there every day for a burger and fries now!! Anyone who likes beef and garlic should try that patty melt! Out.of.this.world.!! The beer was ice cold too which is always a plu